author: stsp
msg: On the 1.6.x-r991534 branch, merge r991534 from trunk.
r991534 modified sandbox.py, which doesn't exist in 1.6.x.
So I've merged those changes into main.py (resolving some conflicts),
removed subtree mergeinfo on main.py, and performed a --record-only merge
of r991534 into the 1.6.x branch root.
merge_tests.py already has subtree mergeinfo on the 1.6.x branch for some
reason, so it was affected by the --record-only merge.
No idea why this subtree mergeinfo exists, but I'll leave it alone for now.
